OL,3,CConstance Marten's partner refuses to
OL,4,Canswer prosecution questions
OL,6,FThe partner of wealthy aristocrat
OL,7,FConstance Marten has refused to answer
OL,8,Fany more questions in his baby
OL,9,Fmanslaughter trial, saying he would
OL,10,Fonly respond to queries "relevant" to
OL,11,Fthe case.
OL,13,FMarten, 38, and Mark Gordon, 50, are
OL,14,Fcharged with the manslaughter of their
OL,15,Fbaby daughter Victoria, who died in a
OL,16,Ftent on the South Downs in early 2023.
OL,18,FThe prosecution alleges Victoria died
OL,19,Ffrom hypothermia or was smothered
OL,20,Fwhile co-sleeping in the "flimsy"
OL,21,Ftent, despite past warnings.
