OL,6,FA high-profile manhunt was launched
OL,7,Fafter the defendants fled their
OL,8,Fburning car near Bolton, Greater
OL,9,FManchester, and went off grid in a bid
OL,10,Fto avoid their fifth child being taken
OL,11,Finto care, the Old Bailey has heard.
OL,13,FOn Friday Gordon, who is representing
OL,14,Fhimself, went into the witness box to
OL,15,Fbe cross-examined by prosecutor Tom
OL,16,FLittle KC.
OL,18,FBut before any questions were asked,
OL,19,Fhe declared: "All right, that's it."
