OL,6,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC warned him that
OL,7,Fjurors could draw inferences from his
OL,8,Fdecision to cut short his evidence.
OL,10,FGordon said he wanted to "discontinue
OL,11,Fmy testimony", adding: "Respectfully,
OL,12,FI will be prone to answer questions
OL,13,Frelevant to the case."
OL,15,FJudge Lucraft then told Gordon that he
OL,16,Fcould return to the back of the court,
OL,17,Fwhere Marten sat in the dock with her
OL,18,Fhead down.
