OL,6,FIn his evidence on Wednesday, Gordon
OL,7,Ftold jurors: "Everybody faces
OL,8,Fchallenges in life."
OL,10,FHe said his mother was a hard-working
OL,11,Fnurse who was passionate and
OL,12,Fempathetic and had instilled
OL,13,F"compassion" in him.
OL,15,FHe had said: "The idea I was
OL,16,Funderprivileged was not the case. My
OL,17,Fmother had two or three houses. She
OL,18,Falways provided for us. She showed me
OL,19,Fempathy."
