OL,6,FGordon had blamed the police manhunt
OL,7,Ffor setting off a series of
OL,8,F"calamitous" events culminating in
OL,9,FVictoria's death.
OL,11,FHe said that he and Marten "put
OL,12,Fourselves out" to ensure the baby's
OL,13,Fwellbeing and "no-one could have
OL,14,Fanticipated" her death.
OL,16,FWeeping in the witness box, Gordon had
OL,17,Fsaid they had been treated like
OL,18,F"monsters" and dragged through mud
OL,19,Flike "scum" over what happened.
