OL,3,CConstance Marten's partner refuses to
OL,4,Canswer prosecution questions
OL,6,FPreviously, Marten has told jurors
OL,7,Fthat the baby died after she "blacked
OL,8,Fout" and fell asleep over her after
OL,9,Ffeeding her.
OL,11,FThe child's body was discovered with
OL,12,Frubbish inside a shopping bag in a
OL,13,Fdisused shed near Brighton, after the
OL,14,Fdefendants were arrested.
OL,16,FMarten and Gordon, of no fixed
OL,17,Faddress, have denied the gross
OL,18,Fnegligence manslaughter of their
OL,19,Fdaughter and causing or allowing her
OL,20,Fdeath between January 4 and February
OL,21,F27 2023.
